Maintainer: <benjamin.renard@inrae.fr>
Description: Tools for detecting, visualizing and estimating shifts, 
    with a specific focus on stage-discharge rating shifts.
    The main methods are described in Darienzo et al. (2021) <https://doi.org/10.1029/2020WR028607>
    and Mansanarez et al. (2019) <https://doi.org/10.1029/2018WR023389>.
    See also BayDERS <https://github.com/MatteoDarienzo/BayDERS> for similar tools, 
    and RatingShiftHappens <https://github.com/Felipemendezrios/RatingShiftHappens> for an older version of this package. 
